# AI-PLC Adaptive Workflow

## Workflow Depth Detection

| Depth | Criteria | Pipeline Behavior | Verification |
|-------|----------|-------------------|-------------|
| Simple | Single domain, 1-2 tasks, known pattern | Stage 1→4 direct | L1 only |
| Standard | Multiple tasks, no Sub-Layer needed | All 4 stages sequential | L1+L2 |
| Complex | Recursive decomposition needed, large scale | All 4 stages + Sub-Layer recursion | L1+L2+L3+NFR |

## Mode Detection

| Mode | Condition | Pipeline |
|------|-----------|----------|
| Direct | One-time execution | Stage 1-4, complete |
| Platform Builder | Building reusable system | Stage 1-4 + Production Skill generation |

## Next Action Routing

| Current State | Next Action |
|---------------|-------------|
| Stage 1 complete | → Stage 2 (Inception) |
| Stage 2 complete | → Stage 3 (Construction) |
| Stage 3 complete | → Stage 4 (Operation) |
| Task complete (more remain) | → Next executable task |
| All tasks complete (Direct) | → Pipeline end |
| All tasks complete (Platform Builder) | → Production Skill generation |
